OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with some rain in the
OL,6,Fwest pushing east and weakening, with
OL,7,Fsome brighter spells developing in the
OL,8,Feast. Some heavier rain reaching the
OL,9,Fwest coast later. Southerly winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening to gale force later
OL,11,Facross the Hebrides.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FBand of heavy rain in west
OL,14,Fcrossing east this evening turning
OL,15,Fshowery tonight the showers becoming
OL,16,Ffrequent and blustery, with gale force
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
