OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with
OL,6,Ffrequent blustery showers and gale
OL,7,Fforce winds. A brighter afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome sunny intervals but still some
OL,9,Fshowers. WInds slowly easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FOvernight rain then blustery showers
OL,13,Fon Thursday, gales. Colder with
OL,14,Fsunshine and showers on Friday, snow
OL,15,Fon high ground. Remaining showery on
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
